message.body: Hello again. I think we spoke yesterday... How's DC? That's a good place to spend the 4th if you're into that sort of thing
Oh right, youre that commie who was headed to the beach, right? Ive moved on from DC, seemed like too rich of a target on a day like today. headed into the
VA mts instead. Hows the beach treating you & your 'girlfriend'?
The mountains sound nice. We're still on our way down to the beack- taking the bus so we can bring our bikes
